#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn4.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "1. Life Span "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 5. Dutiyamārapāsasutta → dutiyapāsasuttaṃ (bj, s1-3) | pāsa (2) (pts1)
msgctxt "sn4.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Dutiyamārapāsasutta "
msgstr "5. Māra’s Snares (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn4.5:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā bārāṇasiyaṃ viharati isipatane migadāye. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Benares, in the deer park at Isipatana. "

msgctxt "sn4.5:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants, "

msgctxt "sn4.5:1.3"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.5:1.4"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ. "
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied. "

msgctxt "sn4.5:1.5"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "The Buddha said this: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.106, pts2ed1.237, sc2
msgctxt "sn4.5:2.1"
msgid "“Muttāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sabbapāsehi ye dibbā ye ca mānusā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I am freed from all snares, both human and divine. "

msgctxt "sn4.5:2.2"
msgid "Tumhepi, bhikkhave, muttā sabbapāsehi ye dibbā ye ca mānusā. "
msgstr "You are also freed from all snares, both human and divine. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.5:2.3"
msgid "Caratha, bhikkhave, cārikaṃ bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya lokānukampāya atthāya hitāya sukhāya devamanussānaṃ. "
msgstr "Wander forth, mendicants, for the welfare and happiness of the people, out of compassion for the world, for the benefit, welfare, and happiness of gods and humans. "

msgctxt "sn4.5:2.4"
msgid "Mā ekena dve agamittha. "
msgstr "Let not two go by one road. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.5:2.5"
msgid "Desetha, bhikkhave, dhammaṃ ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāsetha. "
msgstr "Teach the Dhamma that’s good in the beginning, good in the middle, and good in the end, meaningful and well-phrased. And reveal a spiritual practice that’s entirely full and pure. "

msgctxt "sn4.5:2.6"
msgid "Santi sattā apparajakkhajātikā, assavanatā dhammassa parihāyanti. "
msgstr "There are beings with little dust in their eyes. They’re in decline because they haven’t heard the teaching. "

msgctxt "sn4.5:2.7"
msgid "Bhavissanti dhammassa aññātāro. "
msgstr "There will be those who understand the teaching! "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.5:2.8"
msgid "Ahampi, bhikkhave, yena uruvelā senānigamo tenupasaṅkamissāmi dhammadesanāyā”ti. "
msgstr "I will travel to Uruvelā, the village of Senāni, in order to teach the Dhamma.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.5:2.9"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked went up to the Buddha and addressed him in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn4.5:3.1"
msgid "“Baddhosi sabbapāsehi, "
msgstr "“You’re bound by all snares, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.5:3.2"
msgid "ye dibbā ye ca mānusā; "
msgstr "both human and divine. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.5:3.3"
msgid "Mahābandhanabaddhosi, "
msgstr "You’re bound by the great bond: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.5:3.4"
msgid "na me samaṇa mokkhasī”ti. "
msgstr "you won’t escape me, ascetic!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn4.5:4.1"
msgid "“Muttāhaṃ sabbapāsehi, "
msgstr "“I’m freed from all snares, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.5:4.2"
msgid "Ye dibbā ye ca mānusā; "
msgstr "both human and divine. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.5:4.3"
msgid "Mahābandhanamuttomhi, "
msgstr "I’m freed from the great bonds; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn4.5:4.4"
msgid "Nihato tvamasi antakā”ti. "
msgstr "You’re beaten, terminator!” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn4.5:5.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā … pe … tatthevantaradhāyīti. "
msgstr "Then Māra … vanished right there."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
